 The BaxiBox, the financial platform arm of Capricorn Digital Limited, has kicked off a campaign for its multiple financial services across the country. These include BaxiBox, BaxiPos, BaxiMpos, BaxiPay, Baxi Mobile App and API( Business-to-Business) services. Speaking at the official launch of the campaign, the Managing Director of Capricorn Digital Limited, Degbola Abudu, said the campaign was necessary in order to avail consumers on the unique and innovative services which are tailored to meet the needs of a wide variety of stakeholders including agents, customers and corporate clients. “We have created a one-stop-shop payment ecosystem aimed at providing everyday financial access and solutions to our agents and customers while creating core services that directly impact their daily lives. As a business, we are dedicated to consistently delivering value to our clients through the use of our technology which is a safe, secure and easy way to complete transactions. We aim at simplifying the buying experience for the end consumer, providing speed, convenience, and confidence for the users. “At the heart of the company is innovation and technical excellence, which drives the business to strive to find new ways to create economic value for our agents and customers. We ensure quality, stability, and security across our platforms,” he said. Abudu explained  that with products such as the BaxiBox and BaxiPos which are multifunctional android based devices, and powered by Baxi’s payment solution with one-stop-shop software built in capabilities, enables an end-user to pay for a multitude of digital products and services including electronic airtime, data bundles, utility bills, pay-TV bills, money transfers, withdrawals and more.